Pat Welsh (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pat_Welsh_(actress) 0 Patricia Anderson "Pat" Welsh (née Carroll; February 11, 1915 – January 26, 1995) was an American film actress, known as the raspy voice of E.T. in the 1982 film E.T. the Extra-Terrestrial.
